ygData.messageBody:
Sheesh...lvl 30 really sucks. It's 3 lvls
combined into one, plus 25% more exp since i'm a ranger
(hybrid class). I've spent quite a few nights going solo
against lizard sentinels, defenders, and protectors in
Cazic and i'm only halfway to 31. =(<br><br>BTW for
those of you who haven't noticed, i don't have any
screenshots posted on this site yet. This is because it took
to long to upload the pics. But they'll be up very
soon since i just discovered that they were Bitmaps!!
i tried to upload 2MB pics lol! Some of the pics
are pretty cool - some are battles vs giants and
cyclops, and some are just plain funny. Hope you enjoy
them!
